<view class="page-shell">
  <view class="discover-hero section-card">
    <view class="discover-brand-row">
      <text class="discover-brand">AI House</text>
      <text class="discover-brand-copy">更像真人客服的租房咨询小程序</text>
    </view>
    <view class="discover-title">聊天找房，比自己乱筛更省时间</view>
    <view class="discover-highlight-list">
      <view wx:for="{{productHighlights}}" wx:key="*this" class="discover-highlight-item">{{item}}</view>
    </view>
    <view class="discover-cta-row">
      <button class="btn-primary discover-cta" bindtap="goToAi">立即咨询</button>
      <view class="discover-cta-note">和客服聊两句就能开始</view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="section section-card recommend-shell">
    <view class="section-head">
      <text class="section-title">先看两套推荐</text>
      <text class="section-subtitle">后续会切成真实公开房源</text>
    </view>
    <view wx:if="{{recommendLoading}}" class="recommend-state">正在加载推荐房源...</view>
    <view wx:elif="{{recommendLoadFailed}}" class="recommend-state recommend-state-error">推荐房源加载失败，你也可以先去咨询。</view>
    <view wx:elif="{{recommendCards.length > 0}}" class="recommend-grid">
      <view
        wx:for="{{recommendCards}}"
        wx:key="id"
        class="recommend-card"
        data-id="{{item.id}}"
        bindtap="openDetail"
      >
        <view wx:if="{{item.cover}}" class="recommend-cover-image-wrap">
          <image class="recommend-cover-image" src="{{item.cover}}" mode="aspectFill" />
          <text wx:if="{{item.tags.length > 0}}" class="recommend-tag">{{item.tags[0]}}</text>
        </view>
        <view wx:else class="recommend-cover">
          <text class="recommend-tag">{{item.statusText}}</text>
        </view>
        <view class="recommend-body">
          <text class="recommend-area">{{item.district}}</text>
          <text class="recommend-title">{{item.title}}</text>
          <text class="recommend-detail">{{item.summary}}</text>
          <view class="recommend-price-row">
            <text class="recommend-price">{{item.priceText}}</text>
          </view>
        </view>
      </view>
    </view>
    <view wx:else class="recommend-state">暂时还没有查到推荐房源，先去咨询也很合适。</view>
  </view>

  <view class="search-shell section-card">
    <view class="section-head">
      <text class="section-title">未来公开找房入口</text>
      <text class="section-subtitle">接口补齐后直接启用</text>
    </view>
    <view class="search-box">
      <text class="search-text">商圈 / 小区 / 地铁 / 地点</text>
      <text class="search-link">即将开放</text>
    </view>
    <scroll-view class="filter-scroll" scroll-x enhanced show-scrollbar="{{false}}">
      <view class="filter-row">
        <view
          wx:for="{{filterGroups}}"
          wx:key="label"
          class="filter-chip {{item.active ? 'filter-chip-active' : ''}}"
        >
          {{item.label}}
        </view>
      </view>
    </scroll-view>
  </view>

  <view class="smart-bar section">
    <text class="smart-dot"></text>
    <text class="smart-copy">{{smartTip}}</text>
  </view>

  <view class="section section-card discover-showcase-card">
    <view class="section-head">
      <text class="section-title">更适合这样找房</text>
      <text class="section-subtitle">不用一上来填满所有条件</text>
    </view>
    <view class="showcase-grid">
      <view wx:for="{{showCaseCards}}" wx:key="title" class="showcase-item">
        <view class="showcase-item-inner">
          <text class="showcase-badge">{{item.badge}}</text>
          <text class="showcase-title">{{item.title}}</text>
          <text class="showcase-meta">{{item.meta}}</text>
          <text class="showcase-price">{{item.price}}</text>
        </view>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="empty-card section-card discover-guide-card">
    <view class="section-title">公开房源列表即将开放</view>
    <view class="empty-copy">现在最顺的方式还是先去咨询，让客服根据你的需求继续帮你找房。</view>
    <button class="btn-primary" bindtap="goToAi">去咨询</button>
  </view>
</view>
